    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Founders 是一款适合 1-16 名玩家的城市建设生存游戏，游戏中的 NPC 具有独特的个性和背景故事。建造并保卫你的定居点，抵御无情的威胁，同时发展你的角色技能。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >存活</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你穿越荒野寻找食物和资源时，与人类、动物和奇幻生物战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/2a80a7b683f5ebcf54f3ea023bfc2140.poster.avif?t=1762199753\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/2a80a7b683f5ebcf54f3ea023bfc2140.webm?t=1762199753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建立定居点并为房屋、商店、公会等建造建筑物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/1ffd705cc414141f64a03b828a376ab1.poster.avif?t=1762199753\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/1ffd705cc414141f64a03b828a376ab1.webm?t=1762199753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩张</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将您的居住地转变为大都市。随着您的定居点的发展，它将获得具有独特个性和背景的公民。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/d787138f388785a2be6b407e5fbc17f8.poster.avif?t=1762199753\" width=630 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152110/extras/d787138f388785a2be6b407e5fbc17f8.webm?t=1762199753\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
